Note [ONNX operators that are added/updated from opset 7 to opset 8]
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
New operators:
  Expand

Updated operators:
  Min, Max, Sum, Mean: supports multidirectional broadcasting.
  MaxPool: added optional indices output.
  Scan
Multidirectional broadcasting is not supported in opset 7. This might cause the onnx model to be incorrect, if inputs to max operators have different shapes
Multidirectional broadcasting is not supported in opset 7. This might cause the onnx model to be incorrect, if inputs to min operators have different shapes
